<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.6.4">
<l>ceykiṉṟa kitiyellām yāṉē yeṉṉuñ ceyvāṉiṉ ṟaṉakaḷum yāṉē yeṉṉuñ</l>
<l>ceytumuṉ ṉiṟantaṉavum yāṉē yeṉṉuñ ceykaippaya ṉuṇpēṉum yāṉē yeṉṉuñ</l>
<l>ceyvārkaḷaic ceyvēṉum yāṉē yeṉṉuñ ceyyakama lakkaṇṇa ṉēṟak kolō</l>
<l>ceyyavula kattīrk kivaiyeṉ collukēṉ ceyya kaṉivā yiḷamāṉ ṟiṟattē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“I [am] every action that is done”, she says,</l>
	<l>“and I am what remains to be done”, she says,</l>
<l>“and I am what goes beyond that which has been done before”, she says,</l>
	<l>“and I am the one who eats the fruit of action”, she says,</l>
<l>“and I am the one who makes the actors”, she says,</l>
	<l>while Kaṇṇaṉ , the one with red lotus eyes settles in [her]?</l>
<l>Why will I say these [words] to you upright people of the world,</l>
	<l>concerning [my] young doe with a mouth [like] red fruit?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
